<section class="guideSection">
  <h2>Why Seedlings Benefit From a Timer</h2>

  <p>
    Seedlings respond best to a predictable day and night cycle. Inconsistent lighting can slow growth and lead to weaker plants.
  </p>

  <p>
    A timer removes guesswork and ensures your setup runs the same way every day, even when you are not around.
  </p>
</section>

